decoworld.vanilla.outside

Class ClientWorld

  • java.lang.Object
    • decoworld.vanilla.outside.ClientWorld
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    decoworld.model.world.combat.events.HealthListener, decoworld.model.world.combat.WorldController

    public class ClientWorld
extends java.lang.Object
implements decoworld.model.world.combat.WorldController, decoworld.model.world.combat.events.HealthListener
    A singular class for the client which extends off world. This handles physics and movement of entities and objects. This acts as a controller for decoworld.model (model) and decoworld.gdxmodel (view).
